content.question:
Assume that an array of integer values has been declared as follows and has been initialized.

int[] arr = new int[10];

Which of the following code segments correctly interchanges the value of  arr[0] and  arr[5] ?

choices.label:
int k = arr[5];

arr[0] = arr[5];

arr[5] = k;

int k = arr[0];

arr[0] = arr[5];

arr[5] = k;

content.answer:
int k = arr[0];

arr[0] = arr[5];

arr[5] = k;
